Used romans/rlog and modified in 2 ways 

1) Amended level of bacxktrace from 2 to 3 as have wrapped own logger around rlog
2) Added CheckLevel function to check what traceing level we have set current
   This was done so that if tracing or debug is set then extend details of logging 
   using the RLOG_CALLER_INFO variable.
3) Used own logger wrapper to enable switching out logging if needed in future

